**Prophetic Hag** | Unaligned Align | Limited
__Basics__
The Prophetic Hag can win with any team, unless that team has wronged the hags. The Prophetic Hag can see the current alignment of another player.
__Details__
The Prophetic Hag is one of the hags (`$i hags`).
During the night, the Prophetic Hag may once use their spell to see the current alignment of another player. This check is not affected by any disguises, obstructions or redirections.
Checking a player is an immediate effect.
